mon Croner, 1296 in   Subsidy Rolls   (Horton, Tottington, and Edburton, Sussex); Willelmus Croner, 1379 in   Poll Tax   (South Mundham, Sussex). Alternatively it might be a variant of  <i>Corney</i> with the medial  <i>-r-</i> metathesized."]}]},{"name":"Adam","type":"FIRST","meanings":["Hebrew: The Scripture name, in Hebrew, Adham, signifying 'man;' literally earthy, red earth; Rudolph, however, says the name in Ethiopic means ' to be fair, beautiful.' Hence the nurse-name Addy, little Adam."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Adam Rivington was born in 1300, in Bolton, Lancashire, England, United Kingdom. He had at least 1 daughter with Mrs Adam Rivington."},"et":{"1300–":"1300–Surnud","1305–Female":"1305–Surnud","1335–Female":"1335–Surnud","1300–Male":"1300–Surnud","1305":"1305","1335":"1335","1300":"1300","Bradshaw, Bolton, Lancashire, England":"Bolton, Lancashire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Bradshaw, Lancashire, England, United Kingdom":"Bradshaw, Lancashire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1300–":"1300–Kuollut","1305–Female":"1305–Kuollut","1335–Female":"1335–Kuollut","1300–Male":"1300–Kuollut","1305":"1305","1335":"1335","1300":"1300","Bradshaw, Bolton, Lancashire, England":"Bolton, Lancashire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Bradshaw, Lancashire, England, United Kingdom":"Bradshaw, Lancashire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1300–":"1300–Décédé","1305–Female":"1305–Décédée","1335–Female":"1335–Décédée","1300–Male":"1300–Décédé","1305":"1305","1335":"1335","1300":"1300","Bradshaw, Bolton, Lancashire, England":"Bolton, Lancashire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Bradshaw, Lancashire, England, United Kingdom":"Bradshaw, Lancashire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Adam Rivington est né en 1300, à Bolton, Lancashire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Il a eu au moins 1 fille avec Mrs Adam Rivington."},"de":{"1300–":"1300–Verstorben","1305–Female":"1305–Verstorben","1335–Female":"1335–Verstorben","1300–Male":"1300–Verstorben","1305":"1305","1335":"1335